'''氟康唑'''（{{lang-en|'''Fluconazole'''}}），屬於[[三唑|三唑]]類[[抗真菌药|抗真菌药]]，可用於治療多種[[真菌病|真菌病]]<ref name=AHFS2016>{{cite web|title=Fluconazole|url=https://www.drugs.com/monograph/fluconazole.html|publisher=The American Society of Health-System Pharmacists|access-date=8 December 2016|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220231218/https://www.drugs.com/monograph/fluconazole.html|archive-date=20 December 2016}}</ref>，例如[[念珠菌症|念珠菌症]]、 [[芽生菌病|芽生菌病]]、[[山谷熱|山谷熱]]、[[隱球菌病|隱球菌病]]、[[組織胞漿菌病|組織胞漿菌病]]、[[皮癬菌病|皮癬菌病]]及[[花斑癬|花斑癬]]<ref name=AHFS2016/>。對於罹病風險較高的患者，如：曾接受[[器官移植|器官移植]]、低體重的新生兒、及[[嗜中性白血球低下|嗜中性白血球低下]]等，氟康唑也可以用預防[[念珠菌病|念珠菌病]]<ref name=AHFS2016/>。氟康唑可經[[口服給藥|口服]]或[[靜脈注射|靜脈注射]]給藥<ref name=AHFS2016/>。

氟康唑常見的副作用為嘔吐、腹瀉、紅疹及{{le|轉氨酶升高|elevated transaminases|肝指數上升}}<ref name=AHFS2016/>。嚴重的副作用有[[肝臟疾病|肝臟疾病]]、[[長QT綜合症|長QT綜合症]]、及[[癲癇發作|癲癇發作]]<ref name=AHFS2016/>。使用於懷孕的患者，可能會增加[[流产|流产]]風險；高劑量使用可能會導致新生兒[[先天性障碍|先天性障碍]]<ref name=FDA2016Preg>{{cite web|title=Fluconazole (Diflucan): Drug Safety Communication - FDA Evaluating Study Examining Use of Oral Fluconazole (Diflucan) in Pregnancy|url=https://www.fda.gov/Safety/MedWatch/SafetyInformation/SafetyAlertsforHumanMedicalProducts/ucm497656.htm|website=FDA|access-date=29 April 2016|date=2016-04-26|archive-date=2016-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160429171031/http://www.fda.gov/Safety/MedWatch/SafetyInformation/SafetyAlertsforHumanMedicalProducts/ucm497656.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=AHFS2016/>。氟康唑為[[抗真菌药|抗真菌药]]<ref name=AHFS2016/>，一般認為其透過干擾真菌的[[细胞膜|细胞膜]]合成達成抑制真菌生長的效果<ref name=AHFS2016/>。

氟康唑於1981年獲得專利，於1988年開始商業販售<ref name=Fis503>{{cite book|last1=Fischer|first1=Janos|last2=Ganellin|first2=C. Robin|title=Analogue-based Drug Discovery|date=2006|publisher=John Wiley & Sons|isbn=9783527607495|page=503|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=FjKfqkaKkAAC&pg=PA503|language=en|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170910172625/https://books.google.com/books?id=FjKfqkaKkAAC&pg=PA503|archive-date=2017-09-10}}</ref>。本品名列於[[世界衛生組織基本藥物標準清單|世界衛生組織基本藥物標準清單]]<ref name="WHO21st">{{cite book | vauthors = ((World Health Organization)) | title = World Health Organization model list of essential medicines: 21st list 2019 | year = 2019 | hdl = 10665/325771 | author-link = World Health Organization | publisher = World Health Organization | location = Geneva | id = WHO/MVP/EMP/IAU/2019.06. License: CC BY-NC-SA 3.0 IGO | hdl-access=free }}</ref>，已有[[通用名藥物|學名藥]]<ref name=AHFS2016/>於市面上流通；2019年，於美國最常使用的藥物中排行第133名，共開立逾五百萬劑<ref>{{cite web | title = The Top 300 of 2019 | url = https://clincalc.com/DrugStats/Top300Drugs.aspx | website = ClinCalc | access-date = 16 October 2021 | archive-date = 2020-03-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200318234059/https://clincalc.com/DrugStats/Top300Drugs.aspx | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = Fluconazole - Drug Usage Statistics | website = ClinCalc | url = https://clincalc.com/DrugStats/Drugs/Fluconazole | access-date = 16 October 2021 | archive-date = 2020-07-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200708071510/https://clincalc.com/DrugStats/Drugs/Fluconazole | dead-url = no }}</ref>。



